text: Akenie Adams (born 5 February 1998) is a Guyanese cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Guyana in the 2016–17 Regional Four Day Competition on 21 April 2017. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Guyanese cricketers Category:Guyana cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
